  "title": "Administrator",
  "description": "<ul><li>Ensure fulfilment of scheduled commitments for Operation Team.</li><li>Ensure good planning and execution of schedules / standby team deployment.</li><li>Response service call during office hours and ensure proper recording of reported incident in WhatsApp & D365 systems.</li><li>Meet delivery schedules in data uploading as prescribed by our client and in-house process.</li><li>Familiarisation of System software – D365 System.</li><li>Guarantee correct entries into the system and eliminate gaps in data processing.</li><li>Arrange for parts and services procurement to support operations.</li><li>Ensure good planning and execution of schedules.</li><li>Ensure fulfilment of scheduled commitments for Operation Team and optimise staff utilisation and deployment.</li><li>Any other duties assigned by Assistant Admin Manager.</li></ul>",
